{"tid":1668831,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"金球獎30人名單 雲迪克再戰C斯","createTime":"2019-10-22T08:10:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T22:46:45.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7ceec8c704d135aba0fef0844dc632bafa8adc55","tid":1668831,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T08:10:19.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】2019年金球獎周一公佈30人候選名單，美斯、基斯坦奴朗拿度、雲迪克3名大熱門齊齊入選。<br />\n<br />\n主辦單位法國雜誌《法國足球》宣佈今年金球獎的候選名單，美斯（Lionel Messi）、基斯坦奴朗拿度、雲迪克悉數入選。<br />\n<br />\n30人名單當中，上季歐聯冠軍利物浦成為大戶，合共有7人入選，除了雲迪克之外，還有三叉戟沙拿、沙迪奧文尼、費明奴、中場雲拿當、右閘阿歷山大阿奴、門將阿里遜。金球獎結果將於12月2日在巴黎揭曉。<br />\n<br />\n雲迪克在8月已經榮獲歐洲足協最佳球員，而美斯則在9月成為國際足協最佳球員，C朗暫時未有著落；以該2個選舉為指標的話，相信今次金球獎將是雲迪克跟美斯之爭；若美斯再贏，將歷史性6度獲獎，以1次力壓宿敵C朗。<br />\n<br />\n去年金球獎由摩迪拿下。這名中場魔術師為皇家馬德里完成歐聯3連霸，更帶領克羅地亞國家隊成為世界盃亞軍，打破了美斯、C朗的10年壟斷。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"c3afd023b9852367c38f8ff15c624c1209cd455f","tid":1668831,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T08:10:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/74692467_10157971904628598_1417476290151186432_n.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_oc=AQnJzGaYkgQyJ8pUpYvLx1Nb8mtkQ6K5HLunUqfu2_ZMJnj7m3C1bcB5JWUp_UhOqKI&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=c83bab20c6213733489739b1c2edd605&amp;oe=5E5F8350\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F74692467_10157971904628598_1417476290151186432_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_oc%3DAQnJzGaYkgQyJ8pUpYvLx1Nb8mtkQ6K5HLunUqfu2_ZMJnj7m3C1bcB5JWUp_UhOqKI%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3Dc83bab20c6213733489739b1c2edd605%26oe%3D5E5F8350&h=d4aee270&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9a5d4b33c0b1803c2d4e84657bcb352268bd1b37","tid":1668831,"uid":265168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T08:19:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">快推行動po<br />\n推到有人搞</span></strong></span><br />\n開咗兩個po都仲未上到熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n快啲一齊討論！<br />\n<br />\n[擴大戰線] [行動] 與其嘈加泰集會 不如唔搞呢個<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1668190\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1668190</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f9797e88edd3113e685224467f02483438076c6a","tid":1668831,"uid":34899,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T14:34:47.000Z","msg":"有孫興民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一個asian？"},{"pid":"e8187bf10d6121f56627aab973f53298abb8aa19","tid":1668831,"uid":137912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T14:37:00.000Z","msg":"到底邊個先係大陸叫法<br />\n<br />\n雲迪克?"},{"pid":"ff7f9e9e09c78619d6fd444f612d6776998195a6","tid":1668831,"uid":218659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T22:24:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />馬列斯都有 成季踢過幾多場"},{"pid":"ba77bde485bb1073be756147bdbd571eea6b777a","tid":1668831,"uid":61660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff7f9e9e09c78619d6fd444f612d6776998195a6","tid":1668831,"uid":218659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T22:24:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />馬列斯都有 成季踢過幾多場"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T22:46:09.000Z","msg":"非洲盃冠軍"},{"pid":"59a9fa0782539888af77fa0fed51e3088c74e6b5","tid":1668831,"uid":3194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T22:46:45.000Z","msg":"where is 尼馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}